<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<strong>Grape Flavored Cigars and Funeral Pyres</strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iapetus-the-acausal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5305138); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5305138&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609720560" alt="Iapetus The Acausal" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5305138)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/iapetus-the-acausal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5305138); return false;">Iapetus The Acausal</a></span>. <em>A Requiem for a <a href="/scp-5712">Dying World</a></em></p>
<p>Probably the closest Fifthists will ever be to the &quot;good guys.&quot;<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /></p>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><em>Prior Reading of SCP-5712 is recommended but not required. Further context of prior events will get you more out of this story.</em></p>
